Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.34,0:01:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at these three guys here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.34,0:01:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's some more.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.37,0:01:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my god, another big one.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.37,0:01:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And another big one.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.37,0:01:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.37,0:01:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like Giants.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.37,0:01:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like Giants.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.79,0:01:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.85,0:01:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got big guys today, Doc.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.85,0:01:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Boy, oh boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.93,0:01:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like basketball day, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.09,0:01:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.09,0:01:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.42,0:01:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You're from where?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.42,0:01:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.42,0:02:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.31,0:02:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.09,0:02:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, sweetheart.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.09,0:02:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.09,0:02:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Teamwork.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.09,0:02:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.09,0:02:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, look at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.09,0:02:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.97,0:02:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.97,0:02:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.97,0:02:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.97,0:02:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.97,0:02:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.97,0:03:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.97,0:03:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.97,0:03:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Peace be with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.97,0:03:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.97,0:03:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Doc.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.03,0:03:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, John.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.03,0:03:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.03,0:03:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.03,0:03:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.03,0:03:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.49,0:03:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Doc.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.49,0:03:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, sweetheart.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.49,0:03:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Have we gotten everybody?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.49,0:03:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Did we get everybody?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.49,0:03:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Gloria and Excelsior Steel.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.18,0:03:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not comfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.46,0:03:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,There's the exit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.46,0:03:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,All the books that I've written, I put that on the wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.06,0:03:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,put that on one of the front pages, you know, to warn people. They ignore the warning, and
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.56,0:04:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,then they write me these indignant emails. I warned you right in the beginning. Keep
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.75,0:04:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,out the riffraff. I try to cut out the riffraff at the opening pages. How many people are
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.42,0:04:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,new here for the first time? Uh-huh. Okay. All right. So we try to balance the program
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.24,0:04:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,depending on, you know, the balance of new people with regular attendees. For those that
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.14,0:04:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,are new, we recapitulate many of the charts and things, but we go through them a little
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.85,0:04:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,faster than usual. And then we always leave time for new charts and new understandings.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.39,0:04:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So we try to take care of it in that manner.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.33,0:04:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The best way to do that is to write a note.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.55,0:04:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The best way to learn is by repetition. Dr. Kallenbach always reminds me of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.82,0:05:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Repetition is the best teacher. And after you've heard a thing enough times, it becomes
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.06,0:05:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,a part of you. You know, you just become, without thinking about it, it just becomes
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.50,0:05:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,an assumption. So the repetition is not without its merit and benefit. What seems simple to
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.75,0:05:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,people who have attended these lectures is quite confrontive to people who haven't. So
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.89,0:05:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,therefore, we recapitulate some common ground, familiar ground, before we tackle the new.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.88,0:05:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,One thing we always do is start with, well, we'll start with the slides. I don't know,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.95,0:05:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,how did Jesus make it without slides? I don't know. He had it written on the back of his hand,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.81,0:06:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know. And, blessed are the, well, I can talk spontaneously for an entire day
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.66,0:06:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,around the clock, so everybody knows that, so I don't need the charts. And the charts
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.85,0:06:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,are for self-discipline, so that I don't do that. Yeah. All right. So what I want to start
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.83,0:06:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,with, then, is slide number one.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.42,0:06:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't give this lecture without slide number one. Right now, I'm reading books.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.87,0:06:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to have audio books. And so I'm going back to basics myself. I'm rereading
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.56,0:06:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Power vs. Force right now. That's the first one. I'm going to read all the books in a
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.82,0:06:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,row. And it's fun going back over familiar territory. Except that you see the errors
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.24,0:07:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,you made, you know, because 10 years later, you've accumulated a lot more information.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.52,0:07:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And the main error we made in Power vs. Force was that we didn't have the power to read
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.62,0:07:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Power vs. Force was the presumption that anybody could do the kinesiologic test for
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.85,0:07:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,truth. And the reason I arrived at that erroneous conclusion or impression was because we tried
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.00,0:07:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,it on, you know, a great number of people. And we did videotapes of it, et cetera. But
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.01,0:07:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,all the people that we tried it on were integrists. They all calibrated over 200. You know, friends
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.60,0:07:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,and associates and teachers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.98,0:07:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And spiritual students. We're all over 200. So naturally, it worked for everyone because
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.01,0:07:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,we had a select group. But we weren't aware we had a select group. I was just presuming
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.13,0:07:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,that they represented all of mankind, which is not so. We've discovered belatedly. So
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.81,0:08:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,this is difficult. These people have had with the method is because that but in later, later
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.92,0:08:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,books, we're trying to correct that and point out that, frankly, the number of people who
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.66,0:08:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.66,0:08:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,With any reliability is really quite limited, actually, you know, to a small percentage
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.31,0:08:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,of the world population. However, a group like this attracts people who are over 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.20,0:08:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,So for a group like this, the majority of people will be able to do it. And then there's
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.14,0:08:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,a peculiarity that some people can't do it, like some people can't ride a bicycle, so
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.38,0:08:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,people can't sing, you know what I mean? Not everybody is born with every gift, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.01,0:08:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I was aware of that. I was watching the Winter Olympics.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.08,0:08:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Not everybody is born with certain talents, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.17,0:08:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,They do things I wouldn't even think of doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.62,0:08:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Downhill speed with your skull as the wind...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.36,0:08:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I look at their exposed skull, not even a helmet on it,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.91,0:09:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,and I say, God, it's going to be one mess if they hit the wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.33,0:09:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Courage or foolishness, it's hard to know which.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.26,0:09:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,But I love the Olympics because of the integrity
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.66,0:09:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,and because of the inner strength and valor of the people.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.86,0:09:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Inner strength and valor, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.37,0:09:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,To put yourself out there like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.05,0:09:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, so we arrived with the map of consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.25,0:09:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,and this evolved rather spontaneously, and I've told the story before,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.10,0:09:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,that I was using, I learned kinesiology from John Diamond,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.32,0:09:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and I was testing it out on...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.70,0:09:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,staff at the clinic back east,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.09,0:09:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,and we made certain discoveries.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.20,0:09:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,When I went to teach it to people, I was looking for students.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.03,0:09:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I was going to give a class on kinesiology that night,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.49,0:10:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,and certain things make everybody go weak,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.30,0:10:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,looking at fluorescent lights.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.96,0:10:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You can take anybody, have them look at fluorescent lights,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.29,0:10:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,they're weak, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.99,0:10:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Whole sweet and low over their solar plexus or pesticide,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.70,0:10:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and I grabbed these...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.72,0:10:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,folks, because they were just around the clinic.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.27,0:10:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We had an attitudinal healing center,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.12,0:10:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,and when I went to test them, they didn't go weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.60,0:10:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, whoa, what is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.98,0:10:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody goes weak with fluorescent lights,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.48,0:10:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,but these spiritual students did not.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.53,0:10:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And then we discovered that as your consciousness rises,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.53,0:10:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,your kinesiologic response is different.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.79,0:10:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So we tested that group, we tested a new group of students
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.12,0:10:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,in the Course in Miracles,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.12,0:10:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and they all went weak with fluorescent lights,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.92,0:10:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,et cetera, in the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.62,0:10:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And then after a few months, none of them went weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.37,0:10:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So we saw, I said, wow, wow, wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.30,0:11:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,There's been a major shift in consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.01,0:11:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,in the acupuncture system.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.34,0:11:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The whole person's energy system had shifted.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.14,0:11:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's how we came upon this discovery,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.47,0:11:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and then later calibrated it and put it on a logarithmic scale
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.19,0:11:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,of one to a thousand.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.63,0:11:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,So I just want to recapitulate that,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.91,0:11:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,that not everyone can do it, for reasons as yet unknown.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.63,0:11:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,There's probably karmic elements of which we are unaware also.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.63,0:11:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps people who have violated the truth in the past
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.39,0:11:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,are not allowed karmically to use it
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.51,0:11:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,until they've re-earned the right to use it, perhaps,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.91,0:11:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.82,0:11:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, anyway, on the map of consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.86,0:11:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,we created a logarithmic scale from one to a thousand.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.26,0:11:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And then we discovered that at level 200,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.34,0:11:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,this is the critical level,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.34,0:11:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,level 200 made the difference between truth versus falsehood,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.34,0:12:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,integrity versus non-integrity.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.34,0:12:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And people are often worrying about what their level of consciousness is,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.75,0:12:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and they want us to calibrate them and all such.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.75,0:12:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And I tell them, the only thing you've got to worry about is to get over 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.75,0:12:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Get over 200, and then forget about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.75,0:12:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,because how can you measure devotion, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.75,0:12:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,18 pounds of devotion, 16 pounds of devotion,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.75,0:12:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,how can you measure commitment?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.77,0:12:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,All the things that count, you know, are not really measurable.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.13,0:12:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,A prevailing level of consciousness, however,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.13,0:12:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,influences how you see and experience the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.13,0:12:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And as perception, down here, perception rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.53,0:12:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And as we go up, perception becomes less and less dominant.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.53,0:12:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And instead, we have vision,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.53,0:12:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,because we begin to discern the essence,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.53,0:12:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,which is the difference between the linear and the non-linear.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.53,0:13:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The difficulty with skeptics is because they are stuck in the linear
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.62,0:13:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,and certain fundamental materialism.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.04,0:13:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And as you move up the scale,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.46,0:13:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,the field becomes more and more undifferentiated.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.03,0:13:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It becomes diffuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.03,0:13:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It becomes an overall ambiance.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.03,0:13:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It becomes, eventually, a way of being.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.03,0:13:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So, these lower levels, then,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.10,0:13:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,these lower levels,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.13,0:13:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,dominate half the people in the United States.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.46,0:13:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Half the people, 49%.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.15,0:13:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And 85% of people in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.15,0:13:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, knowing that
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.74,0:13:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,tempers how you respond to the news.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.74,0:13:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You need that information
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.74,0:14:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,in order to handle watching the nightly news.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.74,0:14:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.99,0:14:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the view of God, the view of oneself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.17,0:14:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,These levels all have names.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.17,0:14:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Most of the people in this group are familiar with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.17,0:14:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,These logs are just a shorthand way of saying it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.17,0:14:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the emotion that goes with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.34,0:14:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is the process going on in consciousness itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.34,0:14:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,All the way from
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.40,0:14:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,the very bottom,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.60,0:14:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,enslavement to being freed,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.60,0:14:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,revelation,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.60,0:14:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,all the way to illumination
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.60,0:14:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,and, eventually, enlightenment.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.60,0:14:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,So, we're all familiar with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.70,0:14:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Anybody have any questions about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.62,0:14:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Speak, or forever hold your peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.87,0:14:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not send me any e-mails about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.36,0:14:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Next.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.94,0:14:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Jesus said, easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.94,0:14:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,There wasn't any e-mails.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.94,0:15:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,There wasn't any computers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.91,0:15:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.91,0:15:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,He wouldn't come back again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.91,0:15:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I said, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.65,0:15:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, with the Internet,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.65,0:15:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,that's not number two.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.12,0:15:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That scale, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.33,0:15:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.46,0:15:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody's been fooling around my slides.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.33,0:15:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That scale goes up to 600.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.58,0:15:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,This scale starts at 600.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.58,0:15:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,At 600, there's the transformation of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.58,0:15:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and the levels of enlightenment.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.58,0:15:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Begin at 600.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.58,0:15:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And these we've written about
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.58,0:15:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,in a book coming out at the end of the year,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.58,0:16:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Devotional Non-duality.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.58,0:16:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, enlightenment, these are the expressions.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.58,0:16:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Some of these we recognize
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.58,0:16:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,as the teachers of history.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.67,0:16:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And these are the great avatars
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.67,0:16:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,out of which
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.74,0:16:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,the world's religions have emerged.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.74,0:16:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And then, beyond that,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.74,0:16:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,are the even higher states,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.74,0:16:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,such as archangels, et cetera.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.97,0:16:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That's one thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.97,0:16:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,If an archangel notices you,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.97,0:16:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,it's like you just hit a brick wall
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.05,0:16:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,at 100 miles an hour,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.05,0:16:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,and your life is totally changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.05,0:16:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Enormous power.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.05,0:16:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,50,000 and up we calibrated them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.10,0:16:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.10,0:16:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go to the next slide.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.88,0:16:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,This was done for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.91,0:16:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,This shows the rise of power
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.91,0:16:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,of the...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.91,0:16:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,as you go up the scale.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.91,0:16:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Next one.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.01,0:16:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.01,0:16:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Next one.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.04,0:17:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Because these are familiar,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.04,0:17:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,we won't spend a lot of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.04,0:17:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,This is 78% of the world's population,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.04,0:17:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,you see, is below 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.04,0:17:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is the great mass of people.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.04,0:17:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And therefore,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.04,0:17:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,to be even spiritually interested
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.04,0:17:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,or committed, you can see
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.04,0:17:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,you belong to the minority.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.04,0:17:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Belong to the minority.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.36,0:17:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is how it looks on a graphic.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.36,0:17:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, in the 22% of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.36,0:17:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,that are calibrated over 200,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.36,0:17:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,counterbalance is 78%
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.36,0:17:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,that is below 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.40,0:17:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, the world would self-destruct,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.40,0:17:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,or civilization would self-destruct.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.40,0:17:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So the challenges to our current civilization
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.40,0:17:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,are coming from this group of people here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.40,0:17:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, next.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.55,0:17:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.91,0:17:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Daniel Lyons.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.49,0:17:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Daniel Lyons made this for us
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.49,0:17:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,and sent it to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.49,0:18:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the evolution of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.49,0:18:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,on a time scale.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.48,0:18:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,People say,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.48,0:18:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,what do you think is the future of mankind?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.48,0:18:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, this is the level of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.48,0:18:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,over great expanses of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.48,0:18:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Percent of elapsed time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.48,0:18:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You can see 90% or 85% of elapsed time,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.56,0:18:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,it was still way down here,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.56,0:18:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and suddenly it took off.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.56,0:18:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You can see, despite the world news,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.56,0:18:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,that it's on a very upbeat,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.56,0:18:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,rampant rise.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.33,0:18:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,People lament, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.33,0:18:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,what they consider to be catastrophes in the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.33,0:18:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,not realizing that catastrophes themselves
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.33,0:18:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,can be of great service to spiritual evolution.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.33,0:18:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing gets you closer to God
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.51,0:18:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,than facing the muzzle of a gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.59,0:18:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,During World War II,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.59,0:18:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,the two of us sang,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.59,0:18:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and they're looking at a live mine
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.59,0:19:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,about to go off.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.46,0:19:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.46,0:19:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's either God or nothing, I'll tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.46,0:19:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,So, in that instant,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.66,0:19:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,you surrender your life, and so.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.66,0:19:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.91,0:19:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,So, therefore, calamity.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.91,0:19:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,See, everybody laments and wrings their hands
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.91,0:19:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,about calamity.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.91,0:19:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,But calamity is the only way
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.91,0:19:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,many people can get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.91,0:19:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Many people cannot get there
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.49,0:19:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,so long as life is smooth, prosperous, etc.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.54,0:19:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And materialism disappears,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.54,0:19:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,quickly,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.54,0:19:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,when you're facing death, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.54,0:19:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.33,0:19:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the evolution of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.33,0:19:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so spectacular
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.33,0:19:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,that we repeat it every lecture.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.33,0:19:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, throughout time,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.63,0:19:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,how consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.63,0:19:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,if we go all the way back
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.63,0:19:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,multi-millions or billions of years,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.63,0:19:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,and track it over the millennia,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.63,0:19:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,you see how the scale of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.63,0:20:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,moves on.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.21,0:20:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,First signs of life,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.43,0:20:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,bacteria and algae,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.43,0:20:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,at that point,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.50,0:20:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,approximately 70% of Earth time
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.50,0:20:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,had already,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.50,0:20:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,70% of the planetary time
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.50,0:20:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,had already evolved
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.50,0:20:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,before the first bacteria appeared
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.50,0:20:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,at calibration level one.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.50,0:20:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The interface of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.91,0:20:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,in organic matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.00,0:20:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So, we'll move next.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.38,0:20:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,How the atheist can explain
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.38,0:20:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,how organic arises from non-organic,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.56,0:20:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,how does organic arise from non-organic,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.56,0:20:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and how does life arise from non-life?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.59,0:20:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Without divinity,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.59,0:20:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,you're pretty stuck for an answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.59,0:20:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it just sort of happened, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.59,0:20:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And the animal kingdom followed
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.59,0:20:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,that evolution of consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.01,0:20:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,and there you see the most ancient animals,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.01,0:20:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,life forms,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.01,0:20:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,calibrated extremely low,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.01,0:21:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,and then they evolve,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.01,0:21:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,and we keep getting higher and higher.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.01,0:21:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We get to the point
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.01,0:21:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,where we say,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.01,0:21:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,we get to the level of vipers,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.77,0:21:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Komodo dragons,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.77,0:21:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,reptiles,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.81,0:21:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,et cetera,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.81,0:21:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,the predatory.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.00,0:21:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And of course, there's corollaries
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.00,0:21:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,in the human domain.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.00,0:21:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,There are people walking around,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.00,0:21:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,in fact, they get big headlines,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.00,0:21:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,they calibrate the same
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.00,0:21:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,as a Komodo dragon,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.00,0:21:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and their effect on your life
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.00,0:21:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,will be identical.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.32,0:21:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we have rodents.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.71,0:21:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Rodents actually calibrate higher
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.71,0:21:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,than serial killers.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.45,0:21:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Serial killers,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.45,0:21:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,you see them on TV all the time,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.45,0:21:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,calibrate around 35.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.45,0:21:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's better to be a rodent.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.45,0:21:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's better to be a rhinoceros.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.45,0:21:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Even a grizzly bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.45,0:21:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but I wouldn't fool around with them,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.45,0:21:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,or water buffaloes either.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.45,0:21:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And then we get up to hippopotamus,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.57,0:21:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,who, as we've said before,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.57,0:22:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,statistically kills more people
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.57,0:22:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,than any other wild animal.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.57,0:22:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You wouldn't think so,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.57,0:22:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,but I guess people are careless
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.57,0:22:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,about hanging out with hippopotamuses.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.30,0:22:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I see them on TV from Africa.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.30,0:22:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,They're there in a canoe
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.30,0:22:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,going by the hippopotamus,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.30,0:22:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and I think, wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.56,0:22:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And then you finally get
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.56,0:22:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,to consciousness level 200,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.56,0:22:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,as in mankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.56,0:22:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a shift of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.56,0:22:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You go from the predator
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.56,0:22:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,to the herbivore.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.56,0:22:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,So here we have the zebra,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.66,0:22:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,the gazelle, the giraffe.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.66,0:22:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You see at 200 and up,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.66,0:22:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,you don't have to kill other living beings
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.66,0:22:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,in order to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.66,0:22:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,So the deer, the bison, the elk,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.66,0:22:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,these are all benign,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.92,0:22:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,relatively benign.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.92,0:22:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, if they get mad at you,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.92,0:22:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,they can give you a hard time,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.92,0:22:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,but in and of themselves,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.92,0:22:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,they're relatively benign.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.92,0:22:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Cats at 240, dogs at 245.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.92,0:22:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And once you adopt an animal,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.01,0:23:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,its consciousness jumps five or ten points.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.01,0:23:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And then you get to gorillas,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.14,0:23:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,some of whom we love,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.14,0:23:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,have become very famous.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.14,0:23:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Some famous gorillas.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.14,0:23:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I think the one of the mother gorilla
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.14,0:23:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,picking up the child
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.14,0:23:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,who fell into her domain there in a zoo.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.14,0:23:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Gently picked up this child
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.14,0:23:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,and put the child aside.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.14,0:23:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It was very heartwarming.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.14,0:23:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody remember that one?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.14,0:23:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.14,0:23:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Very heartwarming.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.14,0:23:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,So here was at 275.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.14,0:23:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Now the exceptions, we said,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.40,0:23:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,there are some animals
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.40,0:23:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,that calibrate as intelligent,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.40,0:23:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,actually can think.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.40,0:23:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,There are black crows,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.40,0:23:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,who can figure out
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.40,0:23:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,how to analyze problems
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.40,0:23:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and come up with solutions.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.40,0:23:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Great parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.40,0:23:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, Coco,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.40,0:23:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,we're all familiar with.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.40,0:23:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And the songbird's song at 500.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.52,0:23:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The cat's purr at 500.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.52,0:23:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The dog's wagging tail at 500.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.52,0:23:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The capacity to respond,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.52,0:23:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,to recognize love.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.61,0:24:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, so the next one.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.68,0:24:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we went on to,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.68,0:24:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,that's the emotional level,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.68,0:24:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,consciousness level.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.97,0:24:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,When you get to 400,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.97,0:24:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,you get the level of the intellect.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.97,0:24:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And so the great philosophers of all time,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.22,0:24:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought it was interesting
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.22,0:24:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,to calibrate all the great books
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.22,0:24:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,of the Western world,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.48,0:24:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,which I happily came into possession
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.48,0:24:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,of a whole set.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.48,0:24:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And you could spend a great deal of time
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.78,0:24:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,reflecting on the implication
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.78,0:24:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,of these various people
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.78,0:24:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and their impact on the world and society.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.92,0:24:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And they're almost all
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.92,0:24:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,in the 400s
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.92,0:24:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,and some even in the high 400s.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.07,0:24:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And those,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.07,0:24:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,in amongst these books,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.07,0:24:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,there was one person
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.07,0:24:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,and then maybe even two
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.10,0:24:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,that probably shouldn't have been there.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.33,0:24:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Engels is certainly out of his realm.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.33,0:24:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,These are all mid-400s.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.33,0:25:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,He's at 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.33,0:25:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And Marx,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.33,0:25:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,the author of Relativism,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.33,0:25:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,calibrates at 130.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.33,0:25:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Now without the,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.33,0:25:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,if you remove Marx and Engels,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.33,0:25:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,then the overall calibration jumps to 465,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.33,0:25:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,shows a major jump.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.33,0:25:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,So even having one
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.33,0:25:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,of a very low energy
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.33,0:25:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,and one that is marginal
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.33,0:25:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,brings down the overall level.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.33,0:25:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And the impact of society
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.88,0:25:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,on relativistic thinking
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.98,0:25:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,has been disastrous.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.98,0:25:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We just came out of the Cold War
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.14,0:25:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,and Vietnam
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.14,0:25:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,and Communist China
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.49,0:25:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,and all the devastation we've seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.49,0:25:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Multi,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.49,0:25:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,multi millions of people dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.49,0:25:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,So people can say,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.49,0:25:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,oh, this is very intellectual.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.80,0:25:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,How can it be intellectual
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.80,0:25:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,when 100 million people die
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.80,0:25:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,because of the impact of just this falsity?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.80,0:25:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hardly,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.80,0:26:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,the intellect and politics and philosophy
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.13,0:26:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,are not irrelevant.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.96,0:26:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,They determine
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.96,0:26:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,the nature of our society.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.96,0:26:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.08,0:26:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,so,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.08,0:26:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,and then we'll go to the next.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.20,0:26:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.20,0:26:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,well,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.20,0:26:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,this is the relationship
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.20,0:26:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,between context
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.20,0:26:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,and content.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.20,0:26:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.51,0:26:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,this is very important to realize
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.68,0:26:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,because this is linear,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.68,0:26:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,this is definable,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.68,0:26:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and the lower mind comprehends this.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.68,0:26:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Then,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.77,0:26:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,this event, however,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.77,0:26:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,occurs in
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.77,0:26:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,approximate field.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.77,0:26:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That's recognized
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.13,0:26:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,with situational
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.13,0:26:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,ethics.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.13,0:26:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's also recognized in court
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.13,0:26:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,that what happens here
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.31,0:26:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,is also influenced
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.31,0:26:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,by the approximate field,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.31,0:26:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,events surrounding it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.31,0:26:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,So,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.31,0:26:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,what would be,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.31,0:26:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,let's say,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.31,0:26:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,a,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.63,0:27:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,what would be a limitation of liberty
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.63,0:27:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,depends on
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.63,0:27:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,the context.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.63,0:27:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,In peacetime,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.63,0:27:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,it would be.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.63,0:27:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,In wartime,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.63,0:27:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,it would just be survival.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.63,0:27:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So whether we say
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.63,0:27:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,a thing is ethical
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.63,0:27:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,or unethical,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.63,0:27:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,good or bad,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.63,0:27:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,legal or illegal,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.63,0:27:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,a crime or not a crime,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.63,0:27:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,depends on the situation,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.63,0:27:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,and even courts,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.63,0:27:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,of course,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.63,0:27:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,acknowledge the influence
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.63,0:27:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,of the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.63,0:27:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,These,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.07,0:27:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,in turn,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.07,0:27:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,then,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.29,0:27:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,are within the overall
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.29,0:27:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,infinite context
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.29,0:27:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,of consciousness itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.29,0:27:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.29,0:27:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,this is the most powerful,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.29,0:27:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,the most dominant,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.29,0:27:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,this becomes influential,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.29,0:27:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,and this is the sequencing
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.29,0:27:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,we see within the linear domain.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.29,0:27:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We see this sequencing
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.72,0:27:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,within the linear domain,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.72,0:27:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,but we're not always aware
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.72,0:27:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,of this,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.72,0:27:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and most people forget
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.72,0:27:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,about this altogether.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.72,0:27:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.72,0:27:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.72,0:27:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.96,0:27:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,we just did a diagram of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.96,0:27:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and we could go back,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.96,0:27:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,go over it again,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.96,0:28:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and this time,
