Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.96,0:28:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,is the ego,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.96,0:28:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,it's linear,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.96,0:28:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,it's limited,
