Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.96,0:28:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,which is measurable,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.96,0:28:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,yes,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.96,0:28:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,and provable.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.22,0:28:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The proximate field,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.22,0:28:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,the somewhat bigger field,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.07,0:28:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,can be understood
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.07,0:28:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,as semi-linear,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.07,0:28:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,semi-limited.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.07,0:28:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's random,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.07,0:28:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,non-linear,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.07,0:28:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,identifiable,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.07,0:28:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,describable,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.07,0:28:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's more diffuse
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.07,0:28:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,and generalized.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.07,0:28:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The overall infinite context,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.07,0:28:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,which is the,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.07,0:28:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,what we drive to,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.07,0:28:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,in,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.07,0:28:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,in all these classes,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.07,0:28:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,what we're trying to do
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.07,0:28:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,is reach
