Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.92,0:29:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,what can I do to advance myself?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.79,0:29:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And I say, well, you can begin by behaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.85,0:29:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Just be polite, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.24,0:29:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But these are things that you don't have to become a,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.47,0:29:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,you don't have to join an ashram.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.93,0:29:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to shave your head and wear sandals.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.82,0:29:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to take any oaths or commit yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.02,0:30:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,These are things that uplift you more than you realize.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.48,0:30:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,To be available to others, to be considerate.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.07,0:30:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Just being considerate, you see, to,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.21,0:30:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,it's very, it's loving to acknowledge other people.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.84,0:30:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Just to acknowledge them.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.92,0:30:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And you can experiment with that in clerks in various stores.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.59,0:30:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And you see, the minute you smile appreciatively and say,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.57,0:30:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,gee, thank you, they just go, bong.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.66,0:30:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, in other words, it's,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.79,0:30:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,to do so is less common than you would think.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.70,0:30:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You would think everybody would thank people for their service.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.74,0:30:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But I've noticed that people are quite bowled over by it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.44,0:30:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So it must not be that common.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.94,0:30:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And to just try to be decent and reliable,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.44,0:30:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,honest, put in hard work, moral and ethical,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.86,0:30:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,to be, you know, relatively kind, easygoing, thoughtful,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.94,0:31:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,to be relatively open, as the suggestion of others, tolerant.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.63,0:31:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You lose your calm, but you come back to it because calmness is where you're happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.85,0:31:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You're happy with calm, and you're not happy with upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.24,0:31:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Try to be respectful of life and cordial towards it, friendly to others.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.48,0:31:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So these are all the common things that people say, well, I know about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.29,0:31:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,They know about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.56,0:31:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you look over them again, it is never too late to re-look at them
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.30,0:31:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,and see where could I be more, perhaps this.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.50,0:31:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Or maybe this, I'm not expressing my appreciation to others.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.13,0:31:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Expressing your appreciation to others is very important.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.26,0:31:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,So we look to see where perhaps we're not being as diplomatic as we could.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.50,0:31:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,And you don't want to be wishy-washy, as nice as one thing and firm as something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.76,0:32:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Nicely firm.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.50,0:32:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, you will have to pay your income tax this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.63,0:32:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,They're friendly about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.14,0:32:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Many years ago, I was audited twice by the IRS, many years ago, back in the 70s or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.33,0:32:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And it was a taxpayer compliance audit.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.42,0:32:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And it was a taxpayer compliance audit. And it was a taxpayer compliance audit.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.88,0:32:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And it was a taxpayer compliance audit. And it was a taxpayer compliance audit.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.11,0:32:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And it was a taxpayer compliance audit.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.27,0:32:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And it was a taxpayer compliance audit.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.40,0:32:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And it was a taxpayer compliance audit.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.35,0:32:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And I got it once, I got it two years in a row.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.49,0:32:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And, but it turned out to be a wonderful time.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.36,0:32:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I laid things out elaborately for the tax man when he came.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.80,0:32:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And coffee and tea, and I had everything laid out so he could explain it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.63,0:32:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And he was just wowed. He went away really happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.10,0:32:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And the best time I was making an appointment with him was Friday afternoon,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.66,0:32:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,because I got to get back to the office.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.59,0:32:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,By 4 o'clock I get started.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.68,0:32:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,By 4 o'clock I get started.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.75,0:32:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,By 4 o'clock I get started.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.90,0:32:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,he was getting itchy feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.25,0:33:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's a little cleverness
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.68,0:33:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I throw in for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.22,0:33:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,They're going to audit you
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.96,0:33:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and do it at home
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.72,0:33:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,until 4 in the afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.73,0:33:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The next year,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.73,0:33:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,by God,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.08,0:33:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,the computer picked me out again.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.36,0:33:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The likelihood of getting
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.21,0:33:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,picked out twice
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.02,0:33:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,was one in a couple of million.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.25,0:33:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And I got it twice in a row.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.00,0:33:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And the second time
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.77,0:33:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,was just as sanguine.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.03,0:33:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,They were just wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.09,0:33:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,They were very nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.90,0:33:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,They were very polite.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.75,0:33:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a very positive
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.83,0:33:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,interchange.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.66,0:33:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I really enjoyed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.75,0:33:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought they were
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.25,0:33:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,quite respectful.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.88,0:33:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And, of course,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.16,0:33:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,who you are, then,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.42,0:33:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,is influencing
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.20,0:33:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,how they behave.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.94,0:33:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,So if you act antagonistic
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.77,0:33:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,and argumentative
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.70,0:33:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and oppositional,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.24,0:33:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,then you'll trigger that
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.42,0:33:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,in the person.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.27,0:33:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So what you try to do
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.55,0:33:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,is help the other person
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.75,0:33:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,accomplish their job
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.03,0:33:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,to the best
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.72,0:33:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,that can be done.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.59,0:33:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So to be as helpful
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.59,0:33:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,to the clerk,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.38,0:33:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,be as helpful
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.88,0:33:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,to the auditor,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.07,0:33:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'll say the headsman.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.92,0:33:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,When he's going to
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.64,0:33:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,chop your head off,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.38,0:33:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,you tell him,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.77,0:34:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,look, don't be nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.64,0:34:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your job.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.51,0:34:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I got complete and total
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.98,0:34:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,faith in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.50,0:34:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And here's a few bucks
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.42,0:34:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,that will,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.57,0:34:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,you want to make him
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.48,0:34:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,the best headsman
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.44,0:34:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,for the crown.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.80,0:34:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You see?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.28,0:34:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, next.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.53,0:34:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, even in that
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.46,0:34:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,kind of a situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.48,0:34:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, there it's
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.07,0:34:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,even more important.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.15,0:34:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.55,0:34:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Because there,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.15,0:34:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,you're being pressured
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.05,0:34:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,to violate, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.73,0:34:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,your own integrity.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.44,0:34:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,No, don't violate.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.53,0:34:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The more you violate,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.80,0:34:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,the more extreme
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.76,0:34:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,the condition,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.57,0:34:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,the less you give in
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.15,0:34:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,to it,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.59,0:34:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,to violating it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.21,0:34:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,These are the,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.46,0:34:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,what the mind does,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.61,0:34:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,99% of the mind
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.23,0:34:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,is silent.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.42,0:34:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So the important thing we,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.88,0:34:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,a couple of important
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.46,0:34:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,things we teach.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.17,0:34:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,One thing is that
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.19,0:34:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,there is no such thing
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.21,0:34:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,as cause and effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.96,0:34:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a mentation
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.98,0:34:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,that you project
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.86,0:34:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,onto phenomena
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.86,0:34:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,within the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.55,0:34:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It does not exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.82,0:34:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no cause
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.71,0:34:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.78,0:35:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead, what happens
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.94,0:35:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,is potentiality
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.21,0:35:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,emerges
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.73,0:35:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,and emerges.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.73,0:35:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What you're seeing
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.84,0:35:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,happening is more like
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.46,0:35:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,the butterfly emerging
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.73,0:35:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,from the cocoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.76,0:35:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, the cocoon
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.32,0:35:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,doesn't cause
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.26,0:35:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,the butterfly.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.84,0:35:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The naive person says,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.23,0:35:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,oh, look,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.69,0:35:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,the cocoon caused
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.57,0:35:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,the butterfly.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.00,0:35:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it's antecedent
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.61,0:35:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,doesn't mean that
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.46,0:35:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,it's causative,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.51,0:35:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.48,0:35:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,and that's a basic fallacy.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.71,0:35:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Because one thing
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.67,0:35:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,precedes another
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.57,0:35:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,does not mean
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.42,0:35:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,that it's causal.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.90,0:35:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It means it's in a
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.19,0:35:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,potentiality
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.57,0:35:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's in a
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.07,0:35:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,reality emerging
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.09,0:35:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,as a witnessable
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.80,0:35:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,actuality.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.36,0:35:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Underneath the mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.01,0:35:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,then,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.48,0:35:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,underneath the mind
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.34,0:35:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,is silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.34,0:35:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The mind comes out
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.63,0:35:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,of silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.63,0:35:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Underneath the thinkingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.05,0:35:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll notice
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.48,0:35:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,the thinkingness
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.32,0:35:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,is really superficial.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.71,0:35:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And you'll notice that
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.03,0:36:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,if you begin to look
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.38,0:36:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,at the silence
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.28,0:36:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,underneath the mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.75,0:36:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The silence does not
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.61,0:36:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,precede the mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.01,0:36:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It underlies it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.63,0:36:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like the
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.59,0:36:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,ocean underlies
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.63,0:36:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,the flying fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.61,0:36:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You can,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.23,0:36:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,even as I'm talking now,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.67,0:36:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,don't worry about
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.53,0:36:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,the talking
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.30,0:36:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,and the words
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.01,0:36:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and understanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.11,0:36:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget that.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.48,0:36:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Just pay attention
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.32,0:36:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,to the fact that
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.13,0:36:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,underneath the listening
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.15,0:36:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and the talking
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.90,0:36:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and the conversation,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.67,0:36:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,the mentation,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.71,0:36:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,that your mind
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.30,0:36:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,is actually silent.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.82,0:36:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.13,0:36:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,99% of your mind
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.38,0:36:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,is silent all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.19,0:36:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Only 1%
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.98,0:36:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,is paying attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.00,0:36:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't pay
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.53,0:36:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,attention to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.30,0:36:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I will not feel
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.94,0:36:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,offended at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.26,0:36:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Ignore the speaker.
