Dialogue: 0,1:35:33.25,1:35:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,to expect just because you're committed
Dialogue: 0,1:35:35.17,1:35:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,to a spiritual way of life
Dialogue: 0,1:35:36.78,1:35:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,or a school of spiritual thought
Dialogue: 0,1:35:39.55,1:35:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,whatever
Dialogue: 0,1:35:39.93,1:35:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,that you will reach instant perfection
Dialogue: 0,1:35:42.78,1:35:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,what you're looking for
Dialogue: 0,1:35:44.85,1:35:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,is likelihoods
Dialogue: 0,1:35:46.10,1:35:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,to increase the propensity
Dialogue: 0,1:35:47.78,1:35:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,and that to me is what the influence of karma is
Dialogue: 0,1:35:51.25,1:35:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,people don't really understand karma
Dialogue: 0,1:35:53.05,1:35:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,karma is
Dialogue: 0,1:35:54.82,1:35:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,it's not deterministic
Dialogue: 0,1:35:57.10,1:35:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,it's
Dialogue: 0,1:35:58.36,1:36:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,potential
Dialogue: 0,1:36:00.28,1:36:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,due to certain karmic proclivities
Dialogue: 0,1:36:03.39,1:36:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,the likelihood of your following
Dialogue: 0,1:36:05.52,1:36:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,certain pathways
Dialogue: 0,1:36:06.51,1:36:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,and making certain yes and no's
Dialogue: 0,1:36:09.39,1:36:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,is greatly increased
Dialogue: 0,1:36:10.48,1:36:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's not determined
Dialogue: 0,1:36:12.48,1:36:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,so karma is not predetermination
Dialogue: 0,1:36:15.47,1:36:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,some people confuse karma
Dialogue: 0,1:36:17.77,1:36:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,with predetermination
Dialogue: 0,1:36:19.14,1:36:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,they also confuse it
Dialogue: 0,1:36:23.03,1:36:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,but we won't go into that
Dialogue: 0,1:36:25.43,1:36:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,karmic then means
Dialogue: 0,1:36:30.14,1:36:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,the propensity
Dialogue: 0,1:36:31.02,1:36:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,the fact that you're a human being
Dialogue: 0,1:36:33.68,1:36:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,is already a major karmic demonstration
Dialogue: 0,1:36:36.69,1:36:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,is it not
Dialogue: 0,1:36:37.46,1:36:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,you weren't born a mouse
Dialogue: 0,1:36:39.39,1:36:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,you weren't born an elephant
Dialogue: 0,1:36:40.56,1:36:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,people say
Dialogue: 0,1:36:43.52,1:36:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,that's genes
Dialogue: 0,1:36:44.47,1:36:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,and how did you get the propensity
Dialogue: 0,1:36:46.63,1:36:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,to inherit those genes
Dialogue: 0,1:36:48.59,1:36:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,so as the Buddha said
Dialogue: 0,1:36:50.68,1:36:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,to be born a human being
Dialogue: 0,1:36:53.85,1:36:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,is a great gift
Dialogue: 0,1:36:55.17,1:36:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,to treasure it
Dialogue: 0,1:36:57.09,1:36:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,not get attached to the linear
Dialogue: 0,1:36:59.90,1:37:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,and to see the essence
Dialogue: 0,1:37:02.10,1:37:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,out of which you have risen
Dialogue: 0,1:37:04.06,1:37:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,the Buddha nature
Dialogue: 0,1:37:05.64,1:37:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,which is not different than God
Dialogue: 0,1:37:07.17,1:37:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,the Buddha calibrated it
Dialogue: 0,1:37:10.96,1:37:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,1,000
Dialogue: 0,1:37:11.69,1:37:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,therefore he realized God
Dialogue: 0,1:37:13.85,1:37:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,as the self
Dialogue: 0,1:37:16.00,1:37:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,and he avoided using the word God
Dialogue: 0,1:37:19.39,1:37:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,because of the ignorance
Dialogue: 0,1:37:20.80,1:37:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,that surrounds it
Dialogue: 0,1:37:22.92,1:37:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,let's just ask
Dialogue: 0,1:37:26.32,1:37:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to just ask something
Dialogue: 0,1:37:27.55,1:37:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,that was in yesterday's paper
Dialogue: 0,1:37:28.82,1:37:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,yesterday's paper
Dialogue: 0,1:37:29.93,1:37:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,the concept that
Dialogue: 0,1:37:32.77,1:37:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,all religious truth and God
Dialogue: 0,1:37:34.84,1:37:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,is amid this
Dialogue: 0,1:37:35.89,1:37:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,copies over 200 verses
Dialogue: 0,1:37:38.21,1:37:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,there was a letter to the editor
Dialogue: 0,1:37:43.31,1:37:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,it says
Dialogue: 0,1:37:43.85,1:37:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,indignantly angry
Dialogue: 0,1:37:46.47,1:37:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,and angry
Dialogue: 0,1:37:46.64,1:37:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,that theology
Dialogue: 0,1:37:51.07,1:37:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,that various things
Dialogue: 0,1:37:53.38,1:37:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,religion
Dialogue: 0,1:37:54.02,1:37:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,spirituality
Dialogue: 0,1:37:55.11,1:37:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,were all myths
Dialogue: 0,1:37:56.11,1:38:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,below a certain level of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,1:38:03.77,1:38:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,you cannot see the truth of it
Dialogue: 0,1:38:06.18,1:38:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and it isn't the person's fault
Dialogue: 0,1:38:07.96,1:38:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,so consciousness is
Dialogue: 0,1:38:09.84,1:38:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,by its own design
Dialogue: 0,1:38:11.06,1:38:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,intrinsically innocent
Dialogue: 0,1:38:12.52,1:38:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,because it does not inherently have
Dialogue: 0,1:38:16.03,1:38:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,the way to tell truth from falsehood
Dialogue: 0,1:38:17.93,1:38:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,the interest in truth from falsehood
Dialogue: 0,1:38:21.27,1:38:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,arises as consciousness
Dialogue: 0,1:38:22.50,1:38:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,level rises
Dialogue: 0,1:38:24.50,1:38:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and again it becomes a propensity
Dialogue: 0,1:38:26.50,1:38:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and a likelihood
Dialogue: 0,1:38:27.50,1:38:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,but not a cause and effect relationship
Dialogue: 0,1:38:29.50,1:38:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,the sense of the self
Dialogue: 0,1:38:35.50,1:38:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,with a capital S
Dialogue: 0,1:38:37.63,1:38:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,is a subtlety
Dialogue: 0,1:38:39.63,1:38:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,an awareness of the field
Dialogue: 0,1:38:41.81,1:38:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,and this sense arises independently
Dialogue: 0,1:38:45.81,1:38:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,of the personal sense of I
Dialogue: 0,1:38:48.89,1:38:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,that which is called I
Dialogue: 0,1:38:53.10,1:38:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,occurs spontaneously within the field
Dialogue: 0,1:38:56.10,1:38:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's spontaneously
Dialogue: 0,1:38:58.32,1:39:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,occurs within the field
Dialogue: 0,1:39:00.32,1:39:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,it's not a decision
Dialogue: 0,1:39:03.00,1:39:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,you can't decide whether or not
Dialogue: 0,1:39:05.00,1:39:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,you can experience your distances
Dialogue: 0,1:39:07.00,1:39:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I
Dialogue: 0,1:39:08.00,1:39:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,it's already a given
Dialogue: 0,1:39:10.00,1:39:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,or you wouldn't be a human being
Dialogue: 0,1:39:12.00,1:39:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I think human beings
Dialogue: 0,1:39:14.31,1:39:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,get born here
Dialogue: 0,1:39:15.31,1:39:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,because they're stuck with a sense of I
Dialogue: 0,1:39:17.31,1:39:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,that claims
Dialogue: 0,1:39:18.31,1:39:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,claims credit for everything
Dialogue: 0,1:39:20.31,1:39:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,claims authorship
Dialogue: 0,1:39:22.31,1:39:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,and therefore this world then
Dialogue: 0,1:39:24.31,1:39:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,is to undo that illusion
Dialogue: 0,1:39:26.31,1:39:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,to undo the illusion
Dialogue: 0,1:39:28.64,1:39:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,that you are a separate independent
Dialogue: 0,1:39:31.64,1:39:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,source of causality
Dialogue: 0,1:39:34.64,1:39:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,a dualistic view of the world
Dialogue: 0,1:39:36.64,1:39:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,so to transcend linearity and duality
Dialogue: 0,1:39:41.77,1:39:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,to me is the ultimate spiritual purpose
Dialogue: 0,1:39:44.77,1:39:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,of human lifetime
Dialogue: 0,1:39:46.77,1:39:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,evolution of human consciousness
Dialogue: 0,1:39:49.02,1:39:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,is very slow
Dialogue: 0,1:39:51.02,1:39:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,and yet we see from the timetable
Dialogue: 0,1:39:54.02,1:39:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,that it's now exhilarating at a rapid rate
Dialogue: 0,1:39:58.22,1:39:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,why?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:59.22,1:40:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,because the combined spiritual intention
Dialogue: 0,1:40:01.22,1:40:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,is so powerful
Dialogue: 0,1:40:02.22,1:40:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,it's not causal
Dialogue: 0,1:40:04.22,1:40:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,we don't cause things
Dialogue: 0,1:40:06.22,1:40:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,to happen differently out there
Dialogue: 0,1:40:08.22,1:40:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,but our own spiritual intention
Dialogue: 0,1:40:11.22,1:40:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,our own spiritual intention
Dialogue: 0,1:40:13.92,1:40:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,as I watch the people in the
Dialogue: 0,1:40:15.92,1:40:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,in the winter olympics
Dialogue: 0,1:40:18.46,1:40:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,you see
Dialogue: 0,1:40:19.46,1:40:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and you see the incredible feet
Dialogue: 0,1:40:21.52,1:40:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,a triple axial
Dialogue: 0,1:40:22.52,1:40:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and then he falls
Dialogue: 0,1:40:24.52,1:40:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I find myself automatically praying for him
Dialogue: 0,1:40:27.52,1:40:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I just automatically pray for him
Dialogue: 0,1:40:29.52,1:40:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,for his spirits
Dialogue: 0,1:40:31.52,1:40:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I pray for his spirit
Dialogue: 0,1:40:33.52,1:40:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,because the courage that it takes
Dialogue: 0,1:40:35.52,1:40:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,to put yourself out there
Dialogue: 0,1:40:37.52,1:40:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,in front of the TV land of the entire world
Dialogue: 0,1:40:40.52,1:40:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean it takes courage
Dialogue: 0,1:40:43.75,1:40:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,it takes courage
Dialogue: 0,1:40:44.75,1:40:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,so every time they fall
Dialogue: 0,1:40:46.75,1:40:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I always pray for them
Dialogue: 0,1:40:47.75,1:40:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I tell them that was beautiful
Dialogue: 0,1:40:48.75,1:40:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,that was wonderful
Dialogue: 0,1:40:49.75,1:40:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and I love you
Dialogue: 0,1:40:50.75,1:40:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and God loves you
Dialogue: 0,1:40:53.75,1:40:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,pretty soon they'll be vying to fall on the ice
Dialogue: 0,1:40:56.22,1:40:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,and say I don't know
Dialogue: 0,1:40:57.22,1:40:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,every time I fall on the ice
Dialogue: 0,1:40:58.22,1:40:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel so good
Dialogue: 0,1:41:00.22,1:41:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,millions of people all over the world
Dialogue: 0,1:41:04.22,1:41:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,praying for him
Dialogue: 0,1:41:05.22,1:41:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,you know
Dialogue: 0,1:41:06.22,1:41:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,wow I don't know
Dialogue: 0,1:41:07.22,1:41:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel just swell
Dialogue: 0,1:41:10.22,1:41:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,well I noticed they weren't crushed
Dialogue: 0,1:41:12.35,1:41:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,they weren't crushed
Dialogue: 0,1:41:13.35,1:41:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,were they
Dialogue: 0,1:41:14.35,1:41:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,and I think it is the spiritual intention
Dialogue: 0,1:41:16.35,1:41:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,of all of us witnessing them
Dialogue: 0,1:41:18.35,1:41:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,and saluting their courage
Dialogue: 0,1:41:20.35,1:41:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,that they are not crushed
Dialogue: 0,1:41:22.71,1:41:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,most ordinary people
Dialogue: 0,1:41:23.71,1:41:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,when they meet a major defeat
Dialogue: 0,1:41:25.71,1:41:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,become crushed
Dialogue: 0,1:41:26.71,1:41:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,and dispirited
Dialogue: 0,1:41:27.71,1:41:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,do they not
Dialogue: 0,1:41:28.71,1:41:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,and yet to see these people
Dialogue: 0,1:41:30.71,1:41:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,practically ignore it
Dialogue: 0,1:41:31.71,1:41:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,and go right on with it
Dialogue: 0,1:41:33.71,1:41:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,so I think myself
Dialogue: 0,1:41:35.97,1:41:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,it is the encouragement
Dialogue: 0,1:41:37.97,1:41:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,and the energy we pour into these contestants
Dialogue: 0,1:41:41.97,1:41:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,for the courage to get up there
Dialogue: 0,1:41:44.53,1:41:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and do what they do
Dialogue: 0,1:41:45.53,1:41:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and then try things that are so difficult
Dialogue: 0,1:41:48.53,1:41:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and to try to be graceful and beautiful about it
Dialogue: 0,1:41:51.57,1:41:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,at the same time
Dialogue: 0,1:41:52.57,1:41:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I think to do a triple axel
Dialogue: 0,1:41:53.57,1:41:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and also be beautiful about it
Dialogue: 0,1:41:54.57,1:41:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,is something else
Dialogue: 0,1:41:56.57,1:41:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I could do a triple axel
Dialogue: 0,1:41:58.57,1:42:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,but I don't know how beautiful I'd be about it
Dialogue: 0,1:42:01.57,1:42:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,so I think our combined intention of integrity
Dialogue: 0,1:42:06.80,1:42:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,encourages people
Dialogue: 0,1:42:08.80,1:42:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,so valor
Dialogue: 0,1:42:10.80,1:42:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,valor then attracts to it the energy
Dialogue: 0,1:42:12.80,1:42:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,that tends to increase valor
Dialogue: 0,1:42:14.80,1:42:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,so spirituality also means valor
Dialogue: 0,1:42:18.80,1:42:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,it is often misinterpreted as passivity
Dialogue: 0,1:42:21.80,1:42:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,and sort of the wet lily kind of spirituality
Dialogue: 0,1:42:24.93,1:42:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I call it
Dialogue: 0,1:42:25.93,1:42:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,no when the bearer walks up to you
Dialogue: 0,1:42:30.43,1:42:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,you better stand up to the bearer
Dialogue: 0,1:42:33.43,1:42:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,it's time to pull your courage together
Dialogue: 0,1:42:36.68,1:42:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and say oh lord I need help with this bearer
Dialogue: 0,1:42:46.63,1:42:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,alright so then
Dialogue: 0,1:42:49.36,1:42:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,spiritual evolution also means strength
Dialogue: 0,1:42:52.36,1:42:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,strength, courage, valor
Dialogue: 0,1:42:55.36,1:42:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,and it doesn't mean passivity
Dialogue: 0,1:42:58.97,1:43:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,passivity you remember from
Dialogue: 0,1:43:00.97,1:43:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,two verses faulty
Dialogue: 0,1:43:01.97,1:43:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Calvary is quite low
Dialogue: 0,1:43:02.97,1:43:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,passivity actually Calvary is very low
Dialogue: 0,1:43:04.97,1:43:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,it's a misinterpretation
Dialogue: 0,1:43:06.97,1:43:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,because Christ said turn the other cheek
Dialogue: 0,1:43:09.97,1:43:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and that misinterpretation has come down through the centuries
Dialogue: 0,1:43:14.19,1:43:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,that spiritual integrity is passivity
Dialogue: 0,1:43:17.19,1:43:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,so you have to reflect on what he meant
Dialogue: 0,1:43:20.19,1:43:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,by that admonition
Dialogue: 0,1:43:22.39,1:43:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,the experience of the self then
Dialogue: 0,1:43:26.69,1:43:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,is first what you presume to be yourself
Dialogue: 0,1:43:29.69,1:43:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,that's always the starting point
Dialogue: 0,1:43:31.69,1:43:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,the experiencer
Dialogue: 0,1:43:33.69,1:43:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,no matter what we're experiencing
Dialogue: 0,1:43:35.93,1:43:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,we presume that's who we are
Dialogue: 0,1:43:37.93,1:43:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,which always brings up the difficulty
Dialogue: 0,1:43:41.02,1:43:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,between discerning perception from essence
Dialogue: 0,1:43:44.02,1:43:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,we're witnessing then is our perception
Dialogue: 0,1:43:50.53,1:43:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and our perceptions
Dialogue: 0,1:43:52.53,1:43:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,are preconceived images projected onto the world
Dialogue: 0,1:43:55.53,1:44:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,how do you differentiate essence from content
Dialogue: 0,1:44:01.40,1:44:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,how do you
Dialogue: 0,1:44:03.60,1:44:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,how can you tell which is content
Dialogue: 0,1:44:05.60,1:44:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,which is a projection
Dialogue: 0,1:44:07.60,1:44:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,which is illusion
Dialogue: 0,1:44:08.60,1:44:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,and which is reality
Dialogue: 0,1:44:11.81,1:44:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,eventually with spiritual work
Dialogue: 0,1:44:13.81,1:44:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,that capacity
Dialogue: 0,1:44:15.81,1:44:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,to discern
Dialogue: 0,1:44:16.81,1:44:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,the capacity for discernment
Dialogue: 0,1:44:19.61,1:44:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,does develop and opens up
Dialogue: 0,1:44:21.61,1:44:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,so that you can look at the thing
Dialogue: 0,1:44:23.77,1:44:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,you see what its image is
Dialogue: 0,1:44:24.77,1:44:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,you see how the world would see it
Dialogue: 0,1:44:26.77,1:44:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and what the world would say about it
Dialogue: 0,1:44:28.77,1:44:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,think about it
Dialogue: 0,1:44:29.77,1:44:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,value it
Dialogue: 0,1:44:30.77,1:44:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and you see its essence
Dialogue: 0,1:44:32.77,1:44:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,so when we see the performer
Dialogue: 0,1:44:35.77,1:44:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,fall on the ice
Dialogue: 0,1:44:36.77,1:44:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,we don't witness him as a failure
Dialogue: 0,1:44:38.77,1:44:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,we don't witness him as a disgrace
Dialogue: 0,1:44:40.77,1:44:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,we have a passing regret
Dialogue: 0,1:44:42.77,1:44:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and he knew that he was taken out
Dialogue: 0,1:44:44.77,1:44:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and at risk when he did that triple axial
Dialogue: 0,1:44:46.77,1:44:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,when he did the second one
Dialogue: 0,1:44:47.77,1:44:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,because how strong are your ankles anyway
Dialogue: 0,1:44:51.00,1:44:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,they're only human ankles
Dialogue: 0,1:44:57.80,1:44:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,alright
Dialogue: 0,1:44:58.80,1:44:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,so we see the essence
Dialogue: 0,1:44:59.80,1:45:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,so that's what we applaud
Dialogue: 0,1:45:01.80,1:45:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,is the essence
Dialogue: 0,1:45:02.80,1:45:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,the courage
Dialogue: 0,1:45:03.80,1:45:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,the valor
Dialogue: 0,1:45:04.80,1:45:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,within the contestant
Dialogue: 0,1:45:06.80,1:45:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and of course they do the best they can
Dialogue: 0,1:45:09.80,1:45:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,but that's not what the whole game is
Dialogue: 0,1:45:11.80,1:45:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,the whole game is who they are
Dialogue: 0,1:45:13.80,1:45:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,so what we applaud is who they are
Dialogue: 0,1:45:15.80,1:45:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and their capacity to go out there
Dialogue: 0,1:45:18.80,1:45:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and publicly state it
Dialogue: 0,1:45:20.80,1:45:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,because they know the downside
Dialogue: 0,1:45:22.80,1:45:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,is like a hundred million people watching you
Dialogue: 0,1:45:24.80,1:45:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,as you fall
Dialogue: 0,1:45:26.80,1:45:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and yet they got the courage to face that
Dialogue: 0,1:45:28.80,1:45:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,so what we discern now is essence
Dialogue: 0,1:45:31.80,1:45:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,essence
Dialogue: 0,1:45:32.80,1:45:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,it isn't
Dialogue: 0,1:45:33.80,1:45:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really care what their scores are
Dialogue: 0,1:45:35.80,1:45:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I never pay any attention to scores
Dialogue: 0,1:45:37.80,1:45:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,what I get is the heart of the person
Dialogue: 0,1:45:40.80,1:45:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,you get the heart of the people
Dialogue: 0,1:45:42.80,1:45:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,as they are being what they are
Dialogue: 0,1:45:44.80,1:45:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,to the fullest extent
Dialogue: 0,1:45:46.80,1:45:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,so that we salute traditionally
Dialogue: 0,1:45:49.96,1:45:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,in the great games
Dialogue: 0,1:45:51.96,1:45:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,to be able to get one up on the experiencer
Dialogue: 0,1:45:59.21,1:46:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,the perceiver
Dialogue: 0,1:46:01.23,1:46:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,is the trick
Dialogue: 0,1:46:02.23,1:46:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and the way it's done
Dialogue: 0,1:46:04.46,1:46:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,we started to talk about before the break
Dialogue: 0,1:46:07.46,1:46:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,you pull back
Dialogue: 0,1:46:09.56,1:46:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and you see you're not the content
Dialogue: 0,1:46:11.56,1:46:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,you're the witness
Dialogue: 0,1:46:12.56,1:46:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,and you're the watcher
Dialogue: 0,1:46:15.01,1:46:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,then you are not even the witness
Dialogue: 0,1:46:16.01,1:46:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,or the watcher
Dialogue: 0,1:46:18.01,1:46:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,you see that witnessing and watching
Dialogue: 0,1:46:20.01,1:46:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,is happening of its own
Dialogue: 0,1:46:22.01,1:46:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,you don't decide
Dialogue: 0,1:46:23.01,1:46:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,oh I think I will witness and watch
Dialogue: 0,1:46:25.01,1:46:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,the phenomena of this world today
Dialogue: 0,1:46:27.01,1:46:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,that's not a decision you made at all
Dialogue: 0,1:46:30.19,1:46:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,it's happening all of its own
Dialogue: 0,1:46:32.19,1:46:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,so you see how the ego would jump in
Dialogue: 0,1:46:34.19,1:46:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and want to take credit
Dialogue: 0,1:46:36.19,1:46:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,so one way to define the
Dialogue: 0,1:46:38.19,1:46:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,the ego
Dialogue: 0,1:46:40.19,1:46:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,the small
Dialogue: 0,1:46:41.19,1:46:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,the self with a small s
Dialogue: 0,1:46:43.19,1:46:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,is that which is constantly seeking
Dialogue: 0,1:46:45.19,1:46:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,to own claim and take credit for
Dialogue: 0,1:46:49.89,1:46:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,in actuality
Dialogue: 0,1:46:51.89,1:46:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,it doesn't deserve any credit for anything
Dialogue: 0,1:46:54.89,1:46:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,it's not the author of anything
Dialogue: 0,1:46:57.89,1:47:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,it's the witness at best the witness
Dialogue: 0,1:47:02.72,1:47:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,the person will say well I am the observer
Dialogue: 0,1:47:04.72,1:47:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,what I is observing
Dialogue: 0,1:47:06.72,1:47:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,there isn't any I observing
Dialogue: 0,1:47:08.72,1:47:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,observing is happening of observing this
Dialogue: 0,1:47:11.72,1:47:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,as a spontaneous autonomous phenomena
Dialogue: 0,1:47:14.72,1:47:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,so phenomena are occurring
Dialogue: 0,1:47:17.07,1:47:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,autonomously
Dialogue: 0,1:47:19.07,1:47:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,as a consequence of emergence
Dialogue: 0,1:47:21.23,1:47:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,as we said the cocoon
Dialogue: 0,1:47:23.23,1:47:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,becomes the butterfly
Dialogue: 0,1:47:25.23,1:47:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,nothing causes it
Dialogue: 0,1:47:29.53,1:47:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,in the experiential world then is
Dialogue: 0,1:47:31.53,1:47:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,radical subjectivity
Dialogue: 0,1:47:34.53,1:47:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,radical subjectivity
Dialogue: 0,1:47:36.77,1:47:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,you look for the radical subjectivity
Dialogue: 0,1:47:40.14,1:47:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,out of which you experience existence
Dialogue: 0,1:47:43.14,1:47:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,the experiencing of existence
Dialogue: 0,1:47:46.43,1:47:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,then you're only a step away
Dialogue: 0,1:47:48.43,1:47:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,to see that that which is
Dialogue: 0,1:47:51.07,1:47:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,you are
Dialogue: 0,1:47:52.07,1:47:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,is the field out of which experiencing itself
Dialogue: 0,1:47:55.07,1:47:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,is emerging
Dialogue: 0,1:47:56.07,1:47:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,and you can witness the eyes
Dialogue: 0,1:47:59.22,1:48:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,greediness
Dialogue: 0,1:48:00.22,1:48:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,greediness
Dialogue: 0,1:48:01.22,1:48:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,to claim
Dialogue: 0,1:48:02.22,1:48:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,that it is the author of all actions
Dialogue: 0,1:48:04.22,1:48:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,and thoughts
Dialogue: 0,1:48:05.22,1:48:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,etc
Dialogue: 0,1:48:06.22,1:48:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,you can watch its greediness
Dialogue: 0,1:48:08.57,1:48:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,without joining the greediness
Dialogue: 0,1:48:09.57,1:48:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and you merely become witness
Dialogue: 0,1:48:11.57,1:48:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,of the personal I
Dialogue: 0,1:48:13.57,1:48:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,you become witness of the personal I
Dialogue: 0,1:48:16.93,1:48:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,anybody
Dialogue: 0,1:48:18.28,1:48:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,you can all do that
Dialogue: 0,1:48:20.42,1:48:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,from this moment on you can all do that
Dialogue: 0,1:48:23.64,1:48:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,there
